data.description:
# 🏴‍☠️Welcome to CastersMC🏴‍☠️
Looking for a server packed with fun and adventures that is Java, Bedrock, And EaglercraftX compatible? CastersMC is the perfect place to come to. Our server is playable on 1.8-1.21
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ❤️Survival❤️
Survive and climb the ranks in our CrystalPVP Survival gamemode.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 🍞Duels🍞
Join many games inside of this gamemode.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ❤️Lifesteal Anarchy❤️
Survive in a lifesteal anarchy server and steal hearts from that one vampire movie🤷‍♂️ 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🥳We have more game modes to come along the way.🥳

🌊Come be apart of our server today🌊
Ip And Links:

`play.castersmc.org`
